longBusinessSummary: Cedergrenska AB (publ) provides preschool and post-secondary education services. The company operates primary and high schools, marine polytechnic and Psychology program school, kindergartens, and gymnasiums, as well as offers various trainee programs. Cedergrenska AB (publ) was founded in 2017 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
